    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Offering a collector-grade 2004 Honda S2000 AP2. This example features the sought-after F22C1 2.2L DOHC VTEC naturally aspirated inline-four, delivering a high-revving power band and exceptional throttle response. The longitudinal drivetrain is paired with a crisp, close-ratio six-speed manual transmission and a factory Torsen limited-slip differential for optimal power delivery. The chassis maintains perfect structural integrity, supported by an unmolested double-wishbone suspension at all four corners, ensuring razor-sharp turn-in and mechanical grip. This vehicle is in concours condition with all original VIN tags present and zero deviations from factory specifications.",
      "price": 46500.0,
